hr.caellian.flow.data

Interface Flux<S extends FluxType>

  • Type Parameters:
    S - class of Flux Type.
    All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Externalizable, PropertyManager, java.io.Serializable

    public interface Flux<S extends FluxType>
extends java.io.Externalizable, PropertyManager
    Flux is a representation of transferable unit. It extends PropertyManager allowing users to store unit related Properties and manage them easily.
    Since:
    1.0.0
